"text": "-", "bbox": [634.9, 520.5, 641.9, 541.3]}, {"text": "1,593", "bbox": [711.7, 520.5, 758.6, 541.3]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [874.5, 520.5, 881.5, 541.3]}, {"text": "1,593", "bbox": [950.4, 520.5, 997.3, 541.3]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [1087.1, 520.5, 1094.0, 541.3]}, {"text": "Total goodwill . . .", "bbox": [160.5, 553.8, 318.4, 574.7]}, {"text": "$240,541", "bbox": [346.5, 553.8, 424.7, 574.7]}, {"text": "$(657,891)", "bbox": [464.7, 553.8, 556.7, 574.7]}, {"text": "$2,514", "bbox": [584.6, 553.8, 641.9, 574.7]}, {"text": "$895,918", "bbox": [680.5, 553.8, 758.6, 574.7]}, {"text": "$(562,990) $1,458,908", "bbox": [796.4, 553.8, 997.3, 574.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1035.0, 553.8, 1045.4, 574.7]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [1087.1, 553.8, 1094.1, 574.7]}, {"text": "* Financial Services includes the disposal of $1.6 million related to the sale of the retail title operations", "bbox": [202.2, 621.3, 1119.1, 642.2]}, {"text": "acquired with the Centex merger.", "bbox": [202.2, 646.3, 482.0, 667.2]}, {"text": "The Company’s accumulated goodwill impairment losses totaled $1.6 billion and $938.7 million at", "bbox": [202.2, 701.4, 1119.1, 722.2]}, {"text": "December 31, 2010 and 2009, respectively. This includes goodwill and impairments associated with the Centex", "bbox": [160.5, 726.4, 1119.2, 747.2]}, {"text": "merger as well as goodwill and impairments associated with previous acquisitions. The goodwill associated with", "bbox": [160.5, 751.4, 1119.2, 772.2]}, {"text": "such previous acquisitions was fully impaired as of December 31, 2008. The Company records goodwill", "bbox": [160.5, 776.4, 1119.1, 797.2]}, {"text": "impairments to other expense (income), net in the Consolidated Statement of Operations.", "bbox": [160.5, 801.4, 904.5, 822.2]}, {"text": "4.", "bbox": [118.8, 856.5, 134.4, 877.3]}, {"text": "Restructuring", "bbox": [160.5, 856.5, 285.5, 877.3]}, {"text": "The Company has taken a series of actions both in response to the challenging operating environment and in", "bbox": [202.2, 911.4, 1119.2, 932.3]}, {"text": "connection with the Centex merger that were designed to reduce ongoing operating costs and improve operating", "bbox": [160.5, 936.4, 1119.0, 957.3]}, {"text": "efficiencies. As a result of the combination of these actions, the Company incurred total restructuring charges as", "bbox": [160.5, 961.4, 1119.2, 982.3]}, {"text": "summarized below ($000’s omitted):", "bbox": [160.5, 986.4, 469.4, 1007.3]}, {"text": "Total Restructuring Actions", "bbox": [777.8, 1037.4, 1028.1, 1058.2]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [783.1, 1066.6, 824.8, 1087.4]}, {"text": "2009*", "bbox": [876.9, 1066.6, 929.0, 1087.4]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [981.1, 1066.6, 1022.8, 1087.4]}, {"text": "Employee severance benefits . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [202.2, 1099.8, 738.8, 1120.7]}, {"text": "$24,850", "bbox": [770.1, 1099.8, 837.8, 1120.7]}, {"text": "$47,525", "bbox": [869.1, 1099.8, 936.8, 1120.7]}, {"text": "$30,343", "bbox": [968.1, 1099.8, 1035.8, 1120.7]}, {"text": "Lease exit costs . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [202.2, 1124.8, 738.8, 1145.7]}, {"text": "27,356", "bbox": [780.5, 1124.8, 837.8, 1145.7]}, {"text": "23,208", "bbox": [879.5, 1124.8, 936.8, 1145.7]}, {"text": "12,095", "bbox": [978.5, 1124.8, 1035.8, 1145.7]}, {"text": "Other . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [202.2, 1149.8, 738.8, 1170.7]}, {"text": "3,929", "bbox": [790.9, 1149.8, 837.8, 1170.7]}, {"text": "2,283", "bbox": [889.9, 1149.8, 936.8, 1170.7]}, {"text": "3,069", "bbox": [988.9, 1149.8, 1035.8, 1170.7]}, {"text": "$56,135", "bbox": [770.1, 1183.2, 837.8, 1204.0]}, {"text": "$73,016", "bbox": [869.1, 1183.2, 936.8, 1204.0]}, {"text": "$45,507", "bbox": [968.1, 1183.2, 1035.8, 1204.0]}, {"text": "* Includes $65.4 million of restructuring costs related to the Centex merger.", "bbox": [202.2, 1235.7, 839.4, 1256.5]}, {"text": "Other than restructuring costs of $5.4 million in 2010 and $8.6 million in 2009 classified within Financial", "bbox": [202.2, 1290.7, 1119.0, 1311.5]}, {"text": "Services expenses, employee severance benefits are included within selling, general and administrative expense", "bbox": [160.5, 1315.7, 1119.1, 1336.6]}, {"text": "while lease exit and other costs are included in other expense (income), net in the Consolidated Statements of", "bbox": [160.5, 1340.7, 1119.2, 1361.6]}, {"text": "Operations. The remaining liability for employee severance benefits and exited leases totaled $8.0 million and", "bbox": [160.5, 1365.7, 1119.2, 1386.6]}, {"text": "$41.7 million, respectively, at December 31, 2010 and $14.2 million and $38.6 million, respectively, at", "bbox": [160.5, 1390.7, 1119.1, 1411.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2009. Substantially all of the remaining liability for employee severance benefits will be paid", "bbox": [160.5, 1415.7, 1119.1, 1436.6]}, {"text": "within the next year, while cash expenditures related to the remaining liability for lease exit costs will be incurred", "bbox": [160.5, 1440.8, 1119.0, 1461.6]}, {"text": "over the remaining terms of the applicable office leases, which generally extend several years. The restructuring", "bbox": [160.5, 1465.8, 1118.9, 1486.6]}, {"text": "costs relate to each of the Company’s reportable segments and were not material to any one segment.", "bbox": [160.5, 1490.8, 1005.3, 1511.6]}, {"text": "66", "bbox": [608.6, 1540.8, 629.4, 1561.6]}]}